```rs
#[op(fast)]
async fn op_read(
  state: Rc<RefCell<OpState>>,
  rid: ResourceId,
  buf: &mut [u8],
) -> Result<u32, Error> {
  // ...
}
```

The future is scheduled via a fast API call and polled by the event loop after being woken up by its waker.

Easy async
```ts
let c = new Deno.Command("echo", { args: ["foo"] });
let { stdout, stderr } = await c.output();
```

Easy sync
```ts
let c = new Deno.Command("echo", { args: ["foo"] });
let { stdout, stderr } = c.outputSync();
```

Everything else
```ts
const c = new Deno.Command("cat", { stdin: "piped" });
c.spawn();
c.stdout.pipeTo(Deno.openSync("output", { write: true }).writable);

const x = c.stdin.getWriter();
await x.write(new TextEncoder().encode("foobar"));
await x.close();

const s = await c.status;
console.log(s);
```
